{"tid":655530,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"是咩十個男人都有九個都去過一樓一","createTime":"2018-05-06T14:46:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-13T01:05:25.000Z","uid":1426,"like":10,"dislike":84,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"21556c9a149e827cd93a097a616e1797377095d3","tid":655530,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T14:46:20.000Z","msg":"同老公相識到結婚2年幾，老公32歲，我28歲，有個11個月的小朋友！琴晚同老公傾揭，開玩笑問佢有冇去過一樓一，佢竟然話有，21、22歲時去過2、3次！果時我唔知應該俾咩反應，腦一片空白，而且果女人仲大佢20幾歲，咁都啃得落嘅<img src=\"http://n2.hk/d/images/smilies/foshantou/fst_cry.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn2.hk%2Fd%2Fimages%2Fsmilies%2Ffoshantou%2Ffst_cry.gif&h=f240035e&s={SIZE}\" />唔覺得烏遭咩？佢識我之前未冇拍過拖，仲係個處男俾果啲鳳姐<img src=\"http://n2.hk/d/images/smilies/foshantou/fst_shame.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn2.hk%2Fd%2Fimages%2Fsmilies%2Ffoshantou%2Ffst_shame.gif&h=b6bed927&s={SIZE}\" />越唸心裡邊好唔舒服，下次同我愛愛時，好怕自己會介意！但呢係識我之前嘅事，婚後冇再去過，係個顧家嘅好男人！請問你哋啲男人，係咪都有去過的？"},{"pid":"15c6110a628e9dfaa9c6990c8c0f2be4c12491f3","tid":655530,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T14:52:05.000Z","msg":"乜事咁多負評"},{"pid":"85d91ef09192a7b2458fe36fbc10c4e4b891e78a","tid":655530,"uid":81569,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T14:52:24.000Z","msg":"我今年中四 仲係男仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過聽過有同學仔去過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d0149d8cae1eb073e93a155d414980d1bee4125","tid":655530,"uid":131526,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T14:53:31.000Z","msg":"u汪公仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad81b77c90cd7d3f14ac92509cb99e751a3b3614","tid":655530,"uid":104171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T14:55:44.000Z","msg":"是咩"},{"pid":"31cf6d594498764df3de4fce058ac87c65f9cb45","tid":655530,"uid":84154,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,